Full description

Imagine a world where everyone wakes up in their element.
Rooster is the worlds first social, fully customizable wake up experience.
You're about to start looking forward to and loving your alarm.

Rooster has re-invented how people wake up. It's an app that actually makes people excited to hear their alarm in the morning, tailoring new, more enjoyable wake-up experiences for everyone. 

Set the tone for your day: 
* Wake up to surprise voice notes from your friends.
* Choose channel roosters for daily inspiration, jokes, music, and more!

Like the best things in life, Rooster is free.
Have questions, problems, or feedback? Contact us at info@roostermornings.com

